title: DNS Resolution - www.example.com

participant User App as App
participant Stub Resolver as Stub
participant Recursive Resolver as Recur
participant Root NS as Root
participant .com TLD NS as TLD
participant example.com NS as Auth

App->>Stub: getaddrinfo("www.example.com")
Stub->>Recur: Query: www.example.com A?
note over Recur: Check cache - miss
Recur->>Root: www.example.com A?
Root-->>Recur: Referral: .com NS a.gtld-servers.net
note right of Recur: Cache .com NS (TTL 48h)
Recur->>TLD: www.example.com A?
TLD-->>Recur: Referral: example.com NS ns1.example.com
note right of Recur: Cache NS (TTL 2d)
Recur->>Auth: www.example.com A?
Auth-->>Recur: Answer: 93.184.216.34 (TTL 3600)
note right of Recur: Cache A record (TTL 1h)
Recur-->>Stub: 93.184.216.34
Stub-->>App: 93.184.216.34
note over Recur: Subsequent queries from cache
